  "title": "Finance Assistant (Contract)",
  "description": "<p>Finance Assistant (Contract) <br /><strong>Salary:</strong> Up to $2,500/month<br /><strong>Duration:</strong> 3-month contract, renewable <br /><strong>Work Hours:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Monday–Thursday: 8:30am–5:45pm</p></li><li><p>Friday: 8:30am–5:15pm</p></li><li><p>Lunch: 45 minutes</p></li><li><p>Total: 42 hours/week</p></li></ul><p> <strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Process invoices, reimbursement claims, and other financial matters</p></li><li><p>Ensure accuracy and timeliness in financial documentation</p></li><li><p>Use MS Word and Excel (pivot tables, formulas) for reporting and analysis</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with team members to support finance operations</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Polytechnic Diploma in Accountancy or equivalent</p></li><li><p>2–3 years of accounting experience preferred (fresh grads may be considered)</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office, especially Excel</p></li><li><p>Experience with SAP is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Organized, meticulous, and able to meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, team-oriented, and eager to learn</p></li></ul><p>Send your resume to <a href=\"mailto:carol.heng@paradigmrecruitment.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">carol.heng@paradigmrecruitment.com.sg</a> OR <strong>click apply</strong> <strong>now</strong>. Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Heng Xin Yun (Carol)</p><p>EA Reg No: R25126727</p><p>EA License No: 21C0434</p>",
